						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone near the village gate.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records the installation of the deity <hi rend="bold">Rāmāyi (?)</hi> in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Pingaḷa, Chaitra ba. 9 Saturday,</hi> by <hi rend="bold">Banada-Bōti,</hi> wife of <hi rend="bold">Kāse-Bōva</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Kuḷuvanūr</hi> (modern Kuḷenūr). The record is engraved in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">14-15th century A.D.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
